Content: there are a variety of quantum resistant algos being submitted to NIST for the post-quantum era

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: since CC allows to add new consensus rules to komodo chains, i made it so you need to have a valid dilithium signature to be able to spend funds

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: since komodo architecture allows a custom CC chain to inherit all the rest, in literally a weekend, I created a chain that is able to generate dilithium keypairs, send funds to a pubkey and spend those funds using a privkey

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: unlike other quantum resistant algos, dilithium appears to allow pubkey reuse
